Package: nrsR
Title: R toolkit for Nigerian tax systems, PAYE modeling, and revenue analysis. 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Lawrence", "Garba",
           email = "laws.garba@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "Infosights Consulting")
Description: Tools for computing Nigerian Pay-As-You-Earn (PAYE) income tax 
    under evolving tax regulations. The package supports multiple tax law 
    versions including the Personal Income Tax Act (PITA) and the Nigeria Tax 
    Act (2025). Provides functions for PAYE calculation, payroll estimation, 
    tax band analysis, and comparison across tax regimes.
